data.description: AFFORDABLE FINANCING OPPORTUNITY WITH AN FHA ASSUMABLE LOAN AT 5.625%! Incredible opportunity for primary home ownership on this single family home. Surround yourself in the Colorado Mountains - taking in views of pronghorn, moose and other wildlife - from the wrap around deck. Enjoy open flow layout, engineered wood floors, Vermont Castings wood stove, huge utility storage room & oversized 2 car garage +work area. Beautiful view lot with large fenced back yard. Warm Springs offers a gated community, 7 stocked fishing ponds, endless trails, adjacent national forest, clubhouse, tennis/pickleball court, open space. Recent price reduction lower than last appraisal. Home needs a little TLC, with excellent sweat equity potential. Rare assumable loan provides opportunity for home ownership in a tough market with rising interest rates.
